{"tid":1906432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全國新型肺炎確診個案逾8萬宗　95%新增確診來自武漢","createTime":"2020-03-02T02:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T03:05:53.000Z","uid":66087,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"82a9887dd2e2fc2c171b3c8685469cd30ad313e6","tid":1906432,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:53:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20200302090953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2FNews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20200302090953&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igfY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=0e97873e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/News/live.aspx?NewsId=20200302090953</a><br />\n<br />\n新城電台<br />\n2/3/2020 9:09<br />\n<br />\n內地新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情持續, 全國確診個案首次超過8萬宗, 死亡個案2912宗, 共有4萬4000多人康復出院。<br />\n<br />\n全國過去一日新增202宗確診個案 湖北新增196宗確診個案, 武漢佔193宗; 再多42人死亡, 死者全部來自湖北, 累計死亡個案2803宗。"},{"pid":"352809130f4766a6348e720d115a1d184ce5777e","tid":1906432,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:55:28.000Z","msg":"武漢成個死城都仲爆緊<br />\n究竟之前收埋幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70477d1695d96ffb3d04bcacd15f7baac33253b1","tid":1906432,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:55:45.000Z","msg":"其他省啲數字仲假過湖北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n浙江廣東假撚到呢"},{"pid":"89276a2620ef1f842be3d5d8b5d9bd156e622f78","tid":1906432,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:57:47.000Z","msg":"反正條數都係假既  基本上冇人信 （on9除外）"},{"pid":"3e97c7a2dc8c97fe51ede178e5608d35147dbb35","tid":1906432,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T02:58:17.000Z","msg":"全國確診個案首次超過8萬宗<br />\n<br />\n有語病喎呢句<br />\n累積數過咗8萬就永遠都過8萬<br />\n首次兩個字係多餘，因為唔會有再次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fba7af6b92f8a9636c24